        "created_at": "2020-08-31T23:20:23.754Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I\u2019ve posted a design doc on how we could support multiple storage servers per disk in the Kubernetes Operator. If anyone is interested in this area, I\u2019d love your feedback on the proposed design.</p>\n<p>Design: <a href=\"https://github.com/FoundationDB/fdb-kubernetes-operator/wiki/Multiple-Storage-Servers-per-Disk-Design\">https://github.com/FoundationDB/fdb-kubernetes-operator/wiki/Multiple-Storage-Servers-per-Disk-Design</a></p>",
